				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Holy bump from a dead thread!
<br />
Balance to our existing pets will most likely take place after omens. Our new omens pets are <span style="font-style: italic">supposidly</span> nicely balanced. Further balance issues on them will most likely be dealt with after omens. Remember, even though we are pretty much #1 on oldest classes needing to be rebalanced there are other classes that have asked for balance things and wont see them most likely till after omens. We are not the only ones waiting.
<br />

<br />
Now back to the bump, this has nothing to do with omens of war this was another comparision to beastlord pets and ours. Its nice to see old topics bumped up once in awhile, but please make it for an on topic-good reason. I'm not dissing on you, its just good advice for a new poster  <img src="images/smiles/eusa_angel.gif" alt="Angel" border="0" />
<br />

